{
  "text": "This procedure is nearly the same as that suggested by [CITATION_1] for modeling solar flare statistics. The only difference concerns long-term driving between events. While our approach preserves the continous driving rule of the OFC model, their approach introduces driving in discrete portions \u03c4 .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "58938797"
